reviews.title: Useless
reviews.comment: I\'m not able to use this at all! It force closes every time I select something. Was hoping for an update that would fix the problem. Just going to uninstall.
reviews.author: Barbie B

reviews.title: Cannot use back button on home button
reviews.comment: App stops and has to force close every time (and I mean every single time) you use the back button on my Galaxy SII or the home button on the app. So you can open the app look at one of the features and then have it force close and then open it again to look at another. The interface is pleasant and I like all the features and was excited to use it but unfortunately its hardly usable :/
reviews.author: Briana Shackley

reviews.title: Simple and to the point
reviews.comment: I enjoy the simplicity of it at times I have this one and another more depthy pregnancy app. Sometimes im just not into pictures, and precautions.
reviews.author: Carmalita Andrews

reviews.title: Great app, no UK supplies?
reviews.comment: Great app, however the emails I get are ALL U.S. based. If there was additional stuff for UK, that\'ll be lovely. Cheers!
reviews.author: Richard Conway

reviews.title: Good
reviews.comment: I gave this 4 stars instead 5 because my due date is right but it has my a week farther than I am...so not a huge deal but just annoying
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: It\'s ok...
reviews.comment: I havnt found an app yet that has made me think its what I\'m after. This is no exception. The baby names section is useful, but it says I\'m a week ahead than I really am.
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Pregasoris pregnacy
reviews.comment: I put in my est due date and its telling me 14 wks not 13wk that i am, otherwise would be a good app
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Good app.
reviews.comment: I like this app it does help. I wish it wud show pictures of what the baby looks like as it\'s growing, that would be neat.
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Liking it so far.
reviews.comment: So far so good..I jus installed it last night so we\'ll see how this goes. It has everything right so far :) his hope it stays that way!
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Eeehhhhh
reviews.comment: App was okay love the to do list etc BUT when I enter in my \"estimated birth date\" it jumps to weeks ahead and when I do the lmp (I don\'t expect for it to be EXACT) but its 2 weeks off usually all the other apps are a day or 2 before but this is Hhmm hopefully this prob can be fixed
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.comment: Gestational age is incorrect and there\'s way too much spam ads
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Pregasaurus
reviews.comment: This app is very helpful. I love the checklists. They remind me of very important tasks to prepare for baby that I would otherwise forget.
reviews.author: Tiffany Esposito

reviews.title: Wrong week
reviews.comment: I\'m 6wks 1 day, due January 15th. Every other app seems to get it right but if I enter my due date I get 7 weeks instead of 6. Same with lmp. If it could calculate correctly 5 stars for a simple layout and awesome checklist.
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Not great
reviews.comment: I only got this for the list of weekly tasks and it\'s not a very good list. Plus it\'s poorly written. And it says go on a \"babymoon\" in week 13, a babymoon is a vacation for people having trouble getting pregnant o.O
reviews.author: Jessie Kyle

reviews.title: Love it!
reviews.comment: I love the weekly checklist! With my first pregnancy I didnt know what to do and when and ended up doing so much in my last month that I couldnt enjoy it\'s this keeps me on track and keeps me from stressing! Absloutly love this app and would recomed to any pregnant women!
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Nice little app
reviews.comment: Very usefull.
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Okay app
reviews.comment: Same as other apps find info week to week. Basic. Has issues forcing closing but message appears after u closed the yourself lol

reviews.title: Ok
reviews.comment: Ok app could be better with more features

reviews.title: Awsome :)
reviews.comment: I love this app!  This is my 2nd Pregnecy and this app is keeping up like clock work. Love the list of names and to do. I only wish it would show a pic/grafic of the embryo each week to imagine growth better.
